OL,3,CBurnham finalising plans for
OL,4,Cgovernment before becoming prime
OL,5,Cminister on Monday
OL,7,FAndy Burnham will spend the weekend
OL,8,Fpreparing to become prime minister
OL,9,Fwith allies saying he intends to make
OL,10,Fa "dynamic start" with measures to
OL,11,Fease the cost-of-living squeeze.
OL,13,FThe Labour leader will become prime
OL,14,Fminister on Monday but will begin the
OL,15,Fprocess of moving into Downing Street
OL,16,Fover the weekend.
OL,26,@rD@COUrD@QO]
