PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784432922
OL,3,CBurnham finalising plans for
OL,4,Cgovernment before becoming prime
OL,5,Cminister on Monday
OL,7,FHe said he is still "finalising" his
OL,8,Fcabinet after feverish speculation in
OL,9,FWestminster over his choice of
OL,10,Fchancellor, with allies on Labour's
OL,11,Fleft favouring Ed Miliband but reports
OL,12,Fsuggesting Home Secretary Shabana
OL,13,FMahmood will get the crucial role.
OL,15,FMr Burnham said there had been "too
OL,16,Fmuch" speculation and he would
OL,17,Fannounce his ministerial team on
OL,18,FMonday.
OL,26,@oD@UOUoD@`O]wD@`OUxD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784432922
OL,3,CBurnham finalising plans for
OL,4,Cgovernment before becoming prime
OL,5,Cminister on Monday
OL,7,F"I am finalising those decisions, and
OL,8,FI will come to conclusions very
OL,9,Fshortly, and then I will announce
OL,10,Fthose on Monday," he said.
OL,12,FIn his first speech as Labour leader
OL,13,Fhe said the party was facing its "last
OL,14,Fchance to change" but he promised to
OL,15,F"bring back hope".
OL,17,FHe will become prime minister after
OL,18,FSir Keir Starmer visits Buckingham
OL,19,FPalace to offer his resignation to the
OL,20,FKing on Monday.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@QO]uD@bOUvD@QO]wD@AOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784432922
OL,3,CBurnham finalising plans for
OL,4,Cgovernment before becoming prime
OL,5,Cminister on Monday
OL,7,FMr Burnham will then see the King to
OL,8,F"kiss hands" and be invited to take
OL,9,Fover as prime minister before getting
OL,10,Fthe chance to set out his vision to
OL,11,Fthe country from Downing Street.
OL,13,FHe is expected to use the speech to
OL,14,Fset out plans to give people
OL,15,F"breathing space" on the cost of
OL,16,Fliving and highlight his core theme of
OL,17,Fdevolving power from Whitehall to
OL,18,Fregions across the UK.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@LO]wD@AOUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784432922
OL,3,CBurnham finalising plans for
OL,4,Cgovernment before becoming prime
OL,5,Cminister on Monday
OL,7,FThat devolution process will be driven
OL,8,Ffrom Mr Burnham's "No 10 North" in
OL,9,FManchester, which he is expected to
OL,10,Fvisit during his first week in power.
OL,12,FAllies said Mr Burnham will set out
OL,13,Fpolicies aimed at making people's
OL,14,Flives easier with a promise of
OL,15,Fdelivering tangible change as soon as
OL,16,Fpossible.
OL,26,@pD@SOUpD@_O]
