OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784432922
OL,3,CBurnham finalising plans for
OL,4,Cgovernment before becoming prime
OL,5,Cminister on Monday
OL,7,FHe has already begun to receive
OL,8,Fnational security briefings ahead of
OL,9,Fhis formal appointment and has talked
OL,10,Fto officials about his priorities in
OL,11,Foffice and the first events he will go
OL,12,Fto as prime minister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
